title: Attack on Titan Manga Chapter 1-60
description: This is the complete Attack on Titan (Shingeki no Kyojin) manga, organized into chapters which are also labeled with the official titles.  It covers up to Chapter 60, and is up to date as of time of uploading 08/26/2014.  The chapters are in PDF format, and while I did give them a quick glance for accuracy, I haven't been through them in detail, so if I missed something, let me know.
